1. Install node.js and npm, npm is installed by default with node.js
2. install Angular CLI, to create, build and run the application.
    Command: "npm install -g @angular/cli"
3. Crate a workspace and initial application. Navigate to the target location.
    Command: "ng new app-name"
4. Navigate to the folder of the new created project.
5. To open the project in VS code, use command "code ."
6. Run the appliaction with "ng serve"  
